{"tid":2309640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都好想死 點解決","createTime":"2020-12-02T16:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T16:30:40.000Z","uid":371253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46ad2e0735dc50390c60ab629bbf7d46f4941187","tid":2309640,"uid":371253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"以前未有武肺都唔會成日諗到呢樣野 <br />\n因為長時間都要同人溝通 一有嘢做就冇乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係發現差唔多年半 就開始諗嘢越嚟越灰 <br />\n成日都諗住去自殺  遺書就2019都已經寫定曬係到 覺得自己係到冇乜用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家又面對新環境 又識唔到人 日撚日對住部電腦 想死嘅諗法出曬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係屋企人或者朋友面前就迫自己笑 好開心咁<br />\n但係其他時間就灰曬機 諗自殺 <br />\nWhat can I do<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47174b386bbb9045e66615f33812f8504ff926bc","tid":2309640,"uid":366192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"但係你上個po係叫人唔好自殺 留低做見證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45707d35991f27d7fdde947e5e36ee89d2c8ac80","tid":2309640,"uid":371253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47174b386bbb9045e66615f33812f8504ff926bc","tid":2309640,"uid":366192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"但係你上個po係叫人唔好自殺 留低做見證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"我會覺得大家條命都好珍貴 我條命就冇乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始覺得自己頂唔到落去見證個日 所以想問下大家我應該點"}]}